  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nSTAR ATLAS #207 Breakpoint Reveals & Golden Ticket Winners\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video with Star Atlas updates.\nStar Atlas Recap November 4 2023\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video recapping the latest Star Atlas news.\nMetaverse Nomads #119 Solana Breakpoint Summary\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video replay of their Star Atlas livestream.\nStar Atlas Breakpoint 2023 — The Breakdown!\nRahMega published an article about the Star Atlas Breakpoint presentation.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #104\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nStar Atlas – Ultimate SDU Scanning Tool!\nThe Hologram New Network posted a video about a new SDU scanning tool.\n3D Printed Star Atlas Fimbul GREENADER\nEnigma 42 posted a video about a new 3D printed Star Atlas ship he made.\nSTAR ATLAS #208 NEW SDU SCANNING TOOL!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about more Star Atlas updates.",
